text: Maria Gąsienica Daniel-Szatkowska (5 February 1936 - 1 January 2016) was a Polish alpine skier. She competed at the 1956 Winter Olympics and the 1964 Winter Olympics. She was the sister of fellow Olympians Helena Gąsienica Daniel, Andrzej Gąsienica Daniel and Józef Gąsienica Daniel, as well as fellow competitive skier Franciszek Gąsienica Daniel. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Polish female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Poland Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Alpine skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zakopane
